	<center>
		<h1>Public Key Infrastructure</h1>
		<hr>
	</center>
	<p>PKI enables the following features</p>
	<ul>
            <li>Users to be authenticated to each other</li>
            <li>Encryption of messages over the wire</li>
	</ul>
        <p>Standardization is critical to world- or enterprise-wide usage: see <a href="http://www.ietf.org/html.charters/pkix-charter.html">IETF PKIX working group</a></p>
        <p>Commonly tied to directory information via X.509 certificates</p>
